query:
SELECT id, lastProcessedMessageId, processedAt, totalGamesProcessed 
FROM activity_checkpoint 
WHERE CAST(lastProcessedMessageId AS UNSIGNED) <= 1443874843090223275 
ORDER BY CAST(lastProcessedMessageId AS UNSIGNED) DESC 
LIMIT 1;
